---
import '../styles/global.css';
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/svg+xml" href="/favicon.svg" />
    <link rel="alternate" type="application/rss+xml" title="Sam Hesson's Blog" href="/rss.xml" />
    <meta name="description" content="About Sam Hesson - Software engineer writing about web development, technology, and more" />
    <meta name="author" content="Sam Hesson" />
    <title>About - Sam Hesson</title>
  </head>
  <body class="bg-warm-sand-50 dark:bg-dark-bg-primary">
    <div class="min-h-screen">
      <nav class="bg-warm-sand-100 dark:bg-dark-bg-secondary border-b border-driftwood-200 dark:border-dark-border rounded-b-[24px]">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-4 flex gap-6">
          <a href="/" class="text-lg font-bold text-void-400 dark:text-warm-sand-100 hover:text-living-green-500 dark:hover:text-living-green-300 transition-colors">
            Home
          </a>
          <a href="/about" class="text-lg font-bold text-living-green-500 dark:text-living-green-300">
            About
          </a>
        </div>
      </nav>

      <main class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-12">
        <article>
          <header class="mb-12">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4 text-void-400 dark:text-warm-sand-100" style="letter-spacing: -0.02em;">
              About Me
            </h1>
            <p class="text-xl text-void-200 dark:text-driftwood-200">
              Hi, I'm Sam Hesson. Welcome to my corner of the internet.
            </p>
          </header>

          <div class="prose prose-lg dark:prose-invert max-w-none space-y-6">
            <section class="bg-warm-sand-100 dark:bg-dark-bg-secondary p-8 rounded-[24px] border border-driftwood-300 dark:border-driftwood-300/30 shadow-md mb-8">
              <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-void-400 dark:text-warm-sand-100" style="letter-spacing: -0.02em;">
                Background & Expertise
              </h2>
              <p class="text-void-200 dark:text-driftwood-200 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
                I'm a software engineer passionate about building elegant, user-focused web applications.
                My work spans the full stack, with a particular interest in modern web frameworks,
                developer experience, and the intersection of AI with software development.
              </p>
              <p class="text-void-200 dark:text-driftwood-200 leading-relaxed">
                I believe in writing clean, maintainable code and shipping products that solve real problems.
                Currently exploring the evolving landscape of AI-native development and how it's reshaping
                the way we build software.
              </p>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-8">
              <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-void-400 dark:text-warm-sand-100" style="letter-spacing: -0.02em;">
                Why This Blog?
              </h2>
              <p class="text-void-200 dark:text-driftwood-200 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
                This blog is where I share what I'm learning, building, and thinking about. You'll find:
              </p>
              <ul class="list-disc list-inside space-y-2 text-void-200 dark:text-driftwood-200 ml-4">
                <li>Deep dives into web development frameworks and tools</li>
                <li>Explorations of AI-native development practices</li>
                <li>Thoughts on software engineering culture and practices</li>
                <li>Tutorials and guides for fellow developers</li>
                <li>Experiments with emerging technologies</li>
              </ul>
            </section>

            <section class="mb-8">
              <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-void-400 dark:text-warm-sand-100" style="letter-spacing: -0.02em;">
                What to Expect
              </h2>
              <p class="text-void-200 dark:text-driftwood-200 leading-relaxed">
                I write when inspiration strikes and I have something meaningful to share. Quality over quantity.
                Each post is crafted to provide value, whether that's teaching a new concept, exploring a
                challenging problem, or sharing lessons from real-world projects.
              </p>
            </section>

            <section class="bg-living-green-100 dark:bg-living-green-500/20 p-8 rounded-[24px] border border-living-green-400 dark:border-living-green-400/30 shadow-md">
              <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold mb-4 text-void-400 dark:text-warm-sand-100" style="letter-spacing: -0.02em;">
                Get in Touch
              </h2>
              <p class="text-void-200 dark:text-driftwood-200 mb-4 leading-relaxed">
                I'm always interested in connecting with fellow developers, discussing ideas, or exploring collaboration opportunities.
              </p>
              <div class="space-y-2">
                <p class="text-void-200 dark:text-driftwood-200">
                  <strong class="text-void-400 dark:text-warm-sand-100">Email:</strong>
                  <a href="mailto:hello@samhesson.dev" class="text-living-green-500 dark:text-living-green-300 hover:underline ml-2">
                    hello@samhesson.dev
                  </a>
                </p>
                <p class="text-void-200 dark:text-driftwood-200">
                  <strong class="text-void-400 dark:text-warm-sand-100">GitHub:</strong>
                  <a href="https://github.com/samhesson" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-living-green-500 dark:text-living-green-300 hover:underline ml-2">
                    @samhesson
                  </a>
                </p>
                <p class="text-void-200 dark:text-driftwood-200">
                  <strong class="text-void-400 dark:text-warm-sand-100">LinkedIn:</strong>
                  <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/samhesson" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-living-green-500 dark:text-living-green-300 hover:underline ml-2">
                    /in/samhesson
                  </a>
                </p>
              </div>
              <p class="text-void-200 dark:text-driftwood-200 mt-4 text-sm">
                Feel free to reach out about anything tech-related, collaboration ideas, or just to say hi!
              </p>
            </section>
          </div>
        </article>
      </main>

      <footer class="bg-warm-sand-100 dark:bg-dark-bg-secondary border-t border-driftwood-200 dark:border-dark-border mt-16 rounded-t-[24px]">
        <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 py-8 text-center text-void-200 dark:text-driftwood-200">
          <p>&copy; {new Date().getFullYear()} Sam Hesson. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
      </footer>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
